{"tid":1431622,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韋碧克(黑B)加盟屈福特咁大件事居然冇人講 波台已死","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T04:30:10.000Z","uid":2617,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"927f31cbf60bfef56a1c048b21e781543186a3aa","tid":1431622,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/242/26426554242/26437809213_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F242%2F26426554242%2F26437809213_600x399.jpg&h=95d09964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now Sports-體育】屈福特周五宣佈，簽入自由身的英格蘭國腳韋碧克。<br />\n<br />\n前鋒韋碧克（Danny Welbeck）今夏約滿離開效力了5年的阿仙奴後，一直未有班落，盛傳因為他近年傷患纏身，而且要求的人工太高。<br />\n<br />\n不過，他最終跟屈福特簽約，留在英超。據知韋碧克的周薪高達10萬鎊，成為全隊最高人工的球員，而且要求若之後被賣走，需要收取500萬鎊。韋碧克有機會在周六英超首輪作處子戰，領軍作客愛華頓。<br />\n<br />\n28歲的韋碧克為曼聯青訓產品，2008年首嚐一隊滋味，合共上陣142場，曾於2013年協助球隊贏得英超，2014年以1600萬鎊加盟阿仙奴。他近年傷患甚多，上季僅為兵工廠出戰14場比賽。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=26426554242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D26426554242&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=42faa999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=26426554242</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跟住一齊SHOUT黑B黑B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"403817ae5d4943fe89540382842e1582ce827b50","tid":1431622,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0994e3d9c39447178e7701220720d11